Vulois welcome the bots into the embassy, and showed them around. The 
conference room. The meditating room. The contacting room. The Mess 
Hall("Hey," Vulois said, "Battera likes her fruit.")

He finally came to the quarters section.

"This is where you'll stay. Peace Angels, you may now rest up; I hear 
you had a long journey. If you don't mind, I would like to speak with 
Windrazor alone now."
